"use. You should either find a audio interface that has phono pre-amplifiers "
"built in (one for each deck), use standalone phono pre-amplifiers, or use "
"turntables with built in phono pre-amplifiers."
msgstr "Your audio interface inputs must match the turntable outputs. Turntables output very quiet phono-level outputs that must be amplified for Mixxx to use. You should either find a audio interface that has phono pre-amplifiers built in (one for each deck), use standalone phono pre-amplifiers, or use turntables with built in phono pre-amplifiers."

